flowchart TB
    P[Permissions]:::perm
    R[Role Definitions<br/>Org / Position / Officer]:::role
    O[Organization]:::org
    Pos[Position]:::pos
    Off[Specific Officer]:::off

    %% Inheritance (top-down)
    P --> R
    R --> O
    O --> Pos
    Pos --> Off

    %% Override / Exception (bottom-up)
    Off -. Override .-> Pos
    Pos -. Override .-> O
    O -. Override .-> R

